{"tid":1675332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［牆紙英文合集］WallPaper - 1st English Collective Edition","createTime":"2019-10-25T19:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T16:56:04.000Z","uid":206538,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c4535a41e597d4e64399ec8e82d709e6d432a04c","tid":1675332,"uid":206538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">由於好多巴打反映有好多外國人都有興趣了解香港反送中運動。尤其是身在外國嘅巴打，為了這條國際戰線，今次我們整合了10 期的英文篇章，變成今次的［牆紙英文合集］。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">［牆紙英文合集］主要針對外國人，所以會偏向解釋現時運動上的一些術語、行為及手法，希望可以幫到在國際戰線努力的巴絲。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以下係英文牆紙的簡介，們可以幫手轉胋:</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">WallPaper - 1st English Collective Edition<br />\n<br />\nWallPaper is a record of Hong Kong's protesting journey against government's proposal to allow extradition to mainland China. Much like Lennon Wall, we welcome voices from different people to share their views of the protest.<br />\n<br />\nThe 1st English Collective Edition includes Vol.1-10 from the past 10 weeks, it provides an insight into Hong Kong's political movement such as the people's creative ways of protesting; the issues with some of the government policies and the meaning of the main local slangs and terms used throughout the protest . Our goal is for the world to have a better understanding of Hong Kong's biggest political movement in history. <br />\n<br />\nFeel free to share the articles and discuss with your family and friends.<br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong, Fight for Freedom!</span><br />\n<br />\n今個星期嘅牆紙：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxO1VRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxO1VRr.jpg&h=b8569d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hKtpTC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhKtpTC7.jpg&h=b1f8a023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m25opKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm25opKO.jpg&h=1c29f827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViQLC4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViQLC4P.jpg&h=2beba7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdKTMYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdKTMYa.jpg&h=51f9d115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jr98ARw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJr98ARw.jpg&h=8cf86b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiGbyDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiGbyDc.jpg&h=b2e15fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pmiX4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pmiX4T.jpg&h=2948a85b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnnNRpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnnNRpU.jpg&h=3e5025ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xjHFif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xjHFif.jpg&h=3d5381d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTzHFig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTzHFig.jpg&h=778d3b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8ekrYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8ekrYh.jpg&h=d95b4b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGuHFii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGuHFii.jpg&h=d745926b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPnewpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb